item.description: Please join us for a Level 1 Certification course in EFT (Emotional Freedom Techniques™), the revolutionary healing method that targets unresolved emotional issues and the potential blocks to vibrant love, health and prosperity! The workshop is worth 6 CONTACT HOURS for NURSES/ LNA  in NH and MA and will be facilitated by Approved EFT Practitioner and Teacher, Susan Nordemo, RN, a speaker and workshop presenter with 20 years experience in the healing arts. Sue brings passion, humor and compassion to her audience and you will be sure to have a great time! Cost is $150 per person. PRE-REGISTRATION REQUIRED
